OL,3,C'Belfast Lough could be next Lough
OL,4,CNeagh' - minister issues waste water
OL,5,Cwarning
OL,7,FStormont's minister for Agriculture,
OL,8,FEnvironment and Rural affairs has told
OL,9,FUTV that "Belfast Lough, that could
OL,10,Fbecome the next Lough Neagh" if waste
OL,11,Fwater infrastructure in Northern
OL,12,FIreland is not sorted.
OL,14,FAndrew Muir's comments come as
OL,15,Fcampaigners around Lough Neagh fear a
OL,16,Freturn of blue-green algae amid
OL,17,Fongoing high weather temperatures.
